	<VirtualInstrument CustomTitle="Match multiple Pattern (CSM)" Id="70fdbc7f67ad4b32bbb094f13d6066fd" Reentrancy="Stateful" xmlns="http://www.ni.com/LabVIEW.VI">
		<p.UserDescription xmlns="http://www.ni.com/PlatformFramework">Searches for &lt;b&gt;regular expression&lt;/b&gt; sequentially in &lt;b&gt;string&lt;/b&gt; beginning at &lt;b&gt;offset&lt;/b&gt;. If the function finds the first match, it splits &lt;b&gt;string&lt;/b&gt; into three substrings.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;As a supplement to &lt;b&gt;Match Pattern Function&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;b&gt;regular expression&lt;/b&gt; can include mutiple regular expression, and they are separated by &lt;b&gt;delimiter&lt;/b&gt;.</p.UserDescription>
